Content:
Had a lot of fun with it! Great bot.
However, not without its stumbles:
E.g. &quot;Will good prevail over evil?&quot;
>I don&#x27;t think it will.
&quot;Will evil prevail over good?&quot;
>I don&#x27;t think it will.
&quot;Will good and evil hold in balance?&quot;
>I don&#x27;t think that it will.
